dc_description_s: This ESRI Geodatabase contains polygon features and attribute data tables for census data for the country of Ecuador. The data is derived from INEC Ecuador (Instituto Nacional de Estadisticas y Censos) and was released in 2010. The data contain 40,654 census boundary polygons that each have 217 attributes, and the lowest administrative boundary level represented is Sectores. Refer to the documentation for a list of variables and a translation of variable titles into English. For more information on the census methodology and a glossary of variable categories, go to the INEC website at http://www.ecuadorencifras.gob.ec/.
